	<h4>Better Profile<p>
<span class="label label-success">New</span></p></h4><br />
	<p>
		While still developing, I am quit pleased with the new profile layout.  Members are now able to display their full name along-side their username, as well as write out a small "about me" and display their location if desired.  All of this is now in the user's public profile.
	</p>
</div>
