	<h4>Feed Structure and Design
<p><span class="label label-success">New</span></p></h4><br />
	<p>
  The new feed has many small additions.  First would be the obvious -- the user's private feed design.  The user's feed now has a nice, sleek look.  While I continue to add touch-ups here and there, you can expect the design to look as is.  I have many ideas for multiple types of feed items, which you can read about below.
</p>
</div>
</div>
